---
title: Smart Spicy Shrimp Curry with Buttered Couscous
description: This silky, fragrant curry sauce built on warm spices, tomatoes and cream cheese is sure to delight your palate! A healthy serving of shrimp and a side of light couscous make this meal a wholesome wonder.

Smart is based on a per serving calculation of the recipe's kilocalorie and carbohydrate amount.
